OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA misty, locally foggy morning
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain, especially
OL,7,Fover the hills and moors. The rain
OL,8,Feasing this afternoon allowing some
OL,9,Fbrighter skies to develop, but
OL,10,Fremaining murky around coasts and over
OL,11,Fhills. Feeling warm despite the cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,14,Fwith some patchy rain or drizzle
OL,15,Freturning, especially in the west.
OL,16,FFeeling warm and humid, with murky
OL,17,Fconditions continuing near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
