OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother grey start, with
OL,6,Fpatchy drizzle towards the west. Skies
OL,7,Fwill brighten in the east, though many
OL,8,Fwestern areas holding onto lots of
OL,9,Fcloud. Feeling warm and muggy once
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,13,Fweather in the east on Friday, staying
OL,14,Fcloudier further west with patchy
OL,15,Fdrizzle. Fresher on Saturday with
OL,16,Fbright spells and some showers. More
OL,17,Fsunshine on Sunday, and feeling hotter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
